name: The world is a painting captured on canvas of the universev

metadata.name: What is your inner color ?
metadata.description:
So, as I am spoiled by painting, I see color in everything ... and this is not about chakras)  
Submitted for #ShowYourself contest by Rik Oostenbroek.  
The work was done on his cardboard with acrylic, later transformed into digital painting, like most of my work that you will see here soon.  
Enjoy)
